    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is well-sorted, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and a documented rod bearing service ensuring internal longevity. The powertrain delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and dampers that maintain the chassis's legendary neutral handling balance. Recent valve clearances have been adjusted to factory spec, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for tactile feedback and peak atmospheric performance.",
