    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for 2019 BMW X5 xDrive40i in a stunning Mineral White Metallic finish. This luxury SUV has been consistently maintained and primarily used for long-distance travel, ensuring the engine and transmission remain in smooth, peak operating condition. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, with only minor cosmetic imperfections typical of careful use. Inside, the Canberra Beige Vernasca leather provides a bright, airy atmosphere; the cabin is smoke-free and the upholstery is free of any tears, showing only slight softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. Features include a panoramic moonroof, a crisp 12.3-inch infotainment display, and a premium surround-sound system. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust\u2014recent service includes a full synthetic oil change, brake fluid flush, and a multi-point inspection confirming that all systems are go. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the suspension provides the signature BMW balance of comfort and agility. This is a complete, honest vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
